  proccompose doctor             check prereqs (pheno + Tailscale + Vercel + yq)
  proccompose dry-run          print the full execution graph without running
  proccompose ci                run a fake stack in this sandbox (test mode)
  proccompose deploy \<ref\>   atomic deploy (with rollback safety + deploy lock)
  proccompose release \<ref\> \<pct\>   deploy + cutover in one shot
